metadata.name: Luxuries Are Non Existent
metadata.description:
When time stops, every luxury you've ever desired and have worked to obtain in the future ceases to exist, it becomes untenable.

When time stops, all you have is who you are as a person and how you lived your life until that point.

"When Time Stops" Part 1 of 3

Dimensions : 2600px X 3840px
